y]] - Did research on the phenomenon of [[street-level bureaucracy]]. * [[Norton E. Long]] * [[Theodore J. Lowi]] * [[Niklas Luhmann]] * [[James March]] - One of the developers of the systemic-anarchic perspective of organizational decision making known as the [[Garbage Can Model]]. * [[Roscoe C. Martin]] * [[Karl Marx]] - Believed that government is controlled by those with the most influence on the economy. * [[Renate Mayntz]]
