{{Infobox park | name = Umestan | photo = Umestan (entré).JPG | photo_width = 275 | photo_caption = One of the entrance gates to corporation park Umestan. | map = | map_width = | type = Urban park | location = [[Umeå]], [[Sweden]] | nearest_city = | coords = {{coord|63|50|4|N|20|15|36|E|region:SE|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | coords_ref = | area = | created = 1998 | operator = | visitation_num = | status = | open = Open all year }} '''Umestan''' is a [[business park]] in [[Umeå]], [[Sweden]].
==Description== The business park took over these facilities in 1998, when [[Västerbottens regemente]]s' military operations were shut down. [[Umeå Municipality]] bought the entire area in order to create a business-and knowledge center. The buildings were renovated to meet the needs of modern business regarding comfort, environment and IT capabilities. The business park contains about 40 buildings, which have about 120 different tenants. Around 3&nbsp;000 people visit the area every day.<ref>{{cite web|title=Enterprise and development on historic ground|url=http://umestan.se/om-umestan/english-summary/|work=umestan.se|publisher=Umestan Företagspa|accessdate=3 May 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Historik|url=http://umestan.se/om-umestan/historik/|work=umestan.se|publisher=Umestan Företagspa|accessdate=3 May 2014|language=sv}}</ref>
[[File:Umeå stadsarkiv-1907-I20 under byggnad.jpg|thumb|right|280px|Västerbotten regiment barracks under construction in 1907.]] In 2012 Umeå Municipality sold the park to Lersten for about 470 million kronor.<ref>{{cite web|title=Nu är Umestan såld|url=http://www.folkbladet.nu/309825/nu-ar-umestan-sald|work=folkbladet.nu|publisher=Folkbladet|accessdate=3 May 2014|language=sv}}</ref>
